definitions.definition: A shell or other outer protective layer .
An outer protective covering such as the feathers or skin of an animal, a rind or shell .
The outer layer of an ovule , which develops into the seed coat .

main_definition: A shell or other outer protective layer .
secondary_definitions: ( biology ) An outer protective covering such as the feathers or skin of an animal, a rind or shell .
( botany ) The outer layer of an ovule , which develops into the seed coat .
